<p id="projectPara" class="desc" style="flex-basis:675px;color:black;display:none;">Select this service if you are looking to design and implement a system more efficiently. This service is basically a subset of system development where you must identify problems you would like to fix and opportunities you would like to seize. First, determine requirements for successful completion of the project, including project deliverables and any timelines you would like to keep. Once all the requirements are gathered, I do an in depth analysis to determine how to implement all the requirements of the new system; I will create any applicable charts and diagrams along the way, detailing how the system will be implemented and provide an estimated time of completion. At this point, I assume a supervisory role, advising you and your development team as needed. With the charts and diagrams created during this process, you will be able to plan and manage your project to meet strict deadlines, improve efficiency and rapidly transition your project from a development, to a production environment. Fill out the form below to get started!</p>
